<h3>Best Places to Ski in February</h3>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">If you're looking for powder, plan your holiday for February. Historically one of the snowiest months of the season, due to its reliably perfect snow conditions. Towards the end of the month you'll also enjoy longer days with more time to ski and snowboard and a gentle rise in temperatures.</p>
